dark.description: The component background color lights up the parent's background (as opposed to default behavior which is to darken it); Works unless you specify a CSS background color for it
dark.description_zh: 组件背景颜色会照亮父级的背景（而不是默认行为，即使其变暗）;除非为其指定 CSS 背景色，否则有效
